race.comment: GLASGOW BOY (2) collided with another runner and finished out of the placings when sixth in a Free For All last time (17.48) at this track over 300m. Has the ability and looks a key chance. IDYLLIC PAIGE (1) finds it hard to break through. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (17.20) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Hard to beat again. TRUNKEY REBEL (3) was out of the placings latest but three back was a Grade 5 winner in quick time (16.19) at Cannington in a Grade 5. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. SWEETIE PIE (8) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.
